4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals with no prior knowledge, aiming to become cybersecurity specialists. The program spans 16 weeks, with three live online classes per week and a maximum class size of 16 students. Participants will gain foundational skills in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, along with advanced training in cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence. There are no prerequisites, and the bootcamp content is available in both English and Spanish. Graduates receive an official certificate recognized by various institutions. For more details, visit: https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity. stop